How would I know?

564
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,310
Anyway,

565
00:25:52,330 --> 00:25:54,230
with my brilliant mind,

566
00:25:54,290 --> 00:25:56,270
I can't make such a deduction.

567
00:25:58,120 --> 00:26:01,510
Hong Hui might be skilled in the invisibility technique...

568
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:04,390
and tracking.

569
00:26:05,590 --> 00:26:07,190
You mean...

570
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:09,830
he's Young Master Wang's informant,

571
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:12,230
and he's also protecting Qing Cai?

572
00:26:13,230 --> 00:26:14,630
Protection isn't necessarily the case.

573
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:17,030
People like us...

574
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:20,110
wouldn't let personal feelings...

575
00:26:21,190 --> 00:26:23,080
interfere with our principles.

576
00:26:23,110 --> 00:26:24,150
Of course.

577
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:26,420
We're not ordinary people either.

578
