are going crazy over there

583
00:26:47,130 --> 00:26:48,310
from drinking this.

584
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:51,950
Hu Jiao... said it's pee.

585
00:26:54,070 --> 00:26:55,510
That Pepper.

586
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:59,400
It seems we really are birds of a feather.

587
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:04,740
Why are they crying?

588
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:07,750
They were eating that incredibly spicy food in town

589
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,030
and crying from the heat.

590
00:27:09,140 --> 00:27:10,870
Then they had a bit of this drink,

591
00:27:10,980 --> 00:27:12,000
and somehow

592
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:13,830
it turned into real crying.

593
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:15,950
Sounds like

594
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:18,870
another case of a broken heart.

595
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:22,150
But over whom?

596
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:24,030
Let me ask,

597
00:27:24,510 --> 00:27:27,670
who have they been close to recently?

598
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:35,140
No way.

599
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:38,310
Don't tell me it's you two.

600
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:41,270
I've only been gone for a few days,

601
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:42,430
and you're already like this?

602
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,270
That's a bit much, isn't it?

603
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,110
The one I like

604
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:48,540
likes him,

605
00:27:49,620 --> 00:27:52,870
and as for the one he likes, who knows who she likes.

606
00:27:53,890 --> 00:27:55,230
When you put it that way,

607
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:56,910
it sounds quite complicated.

608
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:02,190
I think those two... like each other.

609
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:04,300
So, after all this,

610
00:28:04,540 --> 00:28:07,270
you two are pining over that pair?

611
00:28:07,790 --> 00:28:10,150
I think you two should really

612
00:28:10,260 --> 00:28:11,150
go sit there

613
00:28:11,170 --> 00:28:12,510
and have a good cry together.

614
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:15,310
It's just a feeling I have. I have no proof.

615
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:17,670
But

616
00:28:17,770 --> 00:28:21,510
a man's intuition might just be right.

617
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:22,510
Wait a minute.

618
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:24,220
She even forcibly kissed Wang Yishao.

619
00:28:24,870 --> 00:28:26,510
Yishao, Yishao?

620
00:28:27,130 --> 00:28:28,390
What? Got kissed against your will?

621
00:28:28,450 --> 00:28:30,430
But recently, those two

622
00:28:30,490 --> 00:28:32,030
haven't been that close.

623
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:35,000
I guess it's the alcohol causing the trouble.

624
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,470
I have a question.

625
00:28:42,730 --> 00:28:43,580
Why's this wine

626
00:28:44,650 --> 00:28:46,670
called "Tears of Lovers"?

627
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:48,990
Tears of Lovers.

628
00:28:49,530 --> 00:28:51,150
Marketing trick for sure.

629
00:28:52,190 --> 00:28:54,230
Just to grab attention.

630
00:28:54,910 --> 00:28:57,070
But the wine itself is actually pretty good.

631
00:28:57,610 --> 00:29:00,990
It has the fresh aroma of the wilderness.

632
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:07,510
-A kindred spirit.
-A kindred spirit.

633
00:29:07,630 --> 00:29:08,350
Come on.

634
00:29:08,570 --> 00:29:09,350
Cheers.

635
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:11,790
What's wrong? Don't you want to drink?

636
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:17,180
Now that Father is safe,

637
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,590
can we go back?

638
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:22,630
What do you think?

639
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:25,750
I know.

640
00:29:26,220 --> 00:29:27,750
I just didn't expect

641
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:30,240
your feelings for each other to be so deep.

642
00:29:35,390 --> 00:29:37,990
Just thinking about how we'd become strangers after this

643
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:41,950
feels like a knife cutting through my heart.

644
00:29:43,160 --> 00:29:44,550
I can't stop thinking about her.

645
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:46,270
I can't forget her.

646
00:29:48,740 --> 00:29:50,710
Actually, I can tell that she feels the same way.

647
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:54,830
She can't let go either.

648
00:29:57,780 --> 00:29:59,110
I just don't understand.

649
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,770
Why does the hatred between our elders

650
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:02,580
have to be passed down to our generation?

651
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,420
What's the point of all that?

652
00:30:04,450 --> 00:30:06,110
Is it just for reputation and power?

653
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,390
That seems so meaningless.

654
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:12,110
Everyone has their own ambitions.

655
00:30:13,060 --> 00:30:14,390
What one likes...

656
00:30:16,010 --> 00:30:17,310
is what's best for them.

657
00:30:19,470 --> 00:30:20,350
That's true.

658
00:30:21,290 --> 00:30:23,820
I have no interest in any of this at all.

659
00:30:24,610 --> 00:30:27,110
Perhaps I simply lack ambition.

660
00:30:28,420 --> 00:30:30,790
Did Master Shang Shan teach you to think this way?

661
00:30:30,810 --> 00:30:32,750
No, he taught me everything—

662
00:30:32,870 --> 00:30:34,270
literature, strategy, and martial arts.

663
00:30:34,320 --> 00:30:36,270
He sees all of these as skills.

664
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:38,500
He says you can never have too many skills.

665
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:41,470
Having skills is one thing; choosing when to use them

666
00:30:41,490 --> 00:30:42,470
is another.

667
00:30:55,230 --> 00:30:56,110
Qing Cai.

668
00:30:58,700 --> 00:30:59,990
I'm setting you free.

669
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:02,230
Go with Gan Pu.

670
00:31:06,120 --> 00:31:07,230
Stop staring at me.

671
00:31:07,570 --> 00:31:09,110
A forced relationship won't bear sweet fruit.

672
00:31:09,330 --> 00:31:10,950
I don't want myself to put up with this.

673
00:31:17,570 --> 00:31:18,590
Actually...

674
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:22,270
I see how devoted you two are to each other.

675
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:25,030
I just can't bring myself...

676
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,670
to tear you apart.

677
00:31:40,530 --> 00:31:41,870
Come on, squat down.

678
00:31:42,070 --> 00:31:42,790
Good.

679
00:31:43,250 --> 00:31:43,990
Hands.

680
00:31:44,110 --> 00:31:45,390
Yes, just like that.

681
